schools.name: Mario C & Joanne Monaco Middle School

data.description:
This elegant home features 4 bed/3 bath 0 car garage!  The garage was converted into a master bedroom or a mother in law headquarters! 
It’s currently rented to a tenant for $1000 per month!  Home has a beautiful sparkling pool and gazebo!  Modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, new flooring, new roof, open floor plan!  It might be considered to have 2 masters with their own bathrooms! Garage conversation has been permitted! The home has safety bars in windows and doors and the front is completely private! No solicitors… backyard is completely private too!  Awesome neighbors!  Located very close to downtown, strip and all shopping facilities as well as freeway access
